<h2 id="text-messages">Text messages</h2>

<p>When choosing to send a text message you should consider:</p>

<ul>
  <li>keeping text messages as short as possible, within one fragment (160 characters), wherever possible for readability</li>
  <li>avoiding abbreviations and links unless necessary</li>
  <li>if this is the right channel for sensitive or clinical information</li>
</ul>

